snippet.title: Jason Momoa and Amber Heard Show Off Their Workout Training for 'Aquaman' | Page Six
snippet.description:
Jason Momoa and Amber Heard showed off their workout and how they've been training for 'Aquaman'. Momoa -- who plays Arthur Curry -- demonstrated his brute strength by scaling one of the toughest rock-climbing walls, courtesy of So iLL, and sharing the video with his millions of Instagram followers. Heard -- who plays Mera -- also shared a video on her Instagram of her training regimen. 

#Aquaman #JasonMomoa #AmberHeard #training #workout
